43#define ATOM_ROM_DATA_PTR 0x20

46#define ATOM_CMD_SETSCLK 0x0A

115struct card_info {
116 struct drm_device *dev;
117 void (* reg_write)(struct card_info *, uint32_t, uint32_t); /* filled by driver */
118 uint32_t (* reg_read)(struct card_info *, uint32_t); /* filled by driver */
119 void (* ioreg_write)(struct card_info *, uint32_t, uint32_t); /* filled by driver */
120 uint32_t (* ioreg_read)(struct card_info *, uint32_t); /* filled by driver */
121 void (* mc_write)(struct card_info *, uint32_t, uint32_t); /* filled by driver */
122 uint32_t (* mc_read)(struct card_info *, uint32_t); /* filled by driver */
123 void (* pll_write)(struct card_info *, uint32_t, uint32_t); /* filled by driver */
124 uint32_t (* pll_read)(struct card_info *, uint32_t); /* filled by driver */
125};
126
127struct atom_context {
128 struct card_info *card;
129 struct mutex mutex;
130 struct mutex scratch_mutex;
131 uint8_t *bios;
132 uint32_t cmd_table, data_table;
133 uint16_t *iio;
134
135 uint16_t data_block;
136 uint32_t fb_base;
137 uint32_t divmul[2];
138 uint16_t io_attr;
139 uint16_t reg_block;
140 uint8_t shift;
141 int cs_equal, cs_above;
142 int io_mode;
143 uint32_t *scratch;
144 int scratch_size_bytes;
145};
146
147extern int atom_debug;
148
149struct atom_context *atom_parse(struct card_info *, void *);
150int atom_execute_table(struct atom_context *, int, uint32_t *);
151int atom_execute_table_scratch_unlocked(struct atom_context *, int, uint32_t *);
152int atom_asic_init(struct atom_context *);
153void atom_destroy(struct atom_context *);
154bool atom_parse_data_header(struct atom_context *ctx, int index, uint16_t *size,
155 uint8_t *frev, uint8_t *crev, uint16_t *data_start);
156bool atom_parse_cmd_header(struct atom_context *ctx, int index,
157 uint8_t *frev, uint8_t *crev);
158int atom_allocate_fb_scratch(struct atom_context *ctx);
159#include "atom-types.h"
160#include "atombios.h"
161#include "ObjectID.h"
162
163#endif
